      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHASING TIME (1) is a first starter from the Henry Norman kennel by Flying Ricciardo out of Serengeti. Gets every chance from the inside draw. Profiles strongly and pay to watch the market closely. LOVE SHAKE (2) is a Brian Smoothy-trained newcomer by Hooked On Scotch out of Strawberry Shake with no trial form to work with. Profiles well but prefer to see a move in betting. SWAN BAY MISS (3) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (17.85) at this track in a Maiden. Well placed here and can atone this time. JED FURY (6) is an improver who can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track when making debut.",
